1665, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Pringle</emphasis>
s.n. [6/4/1882]), Arizona (fide 
<bibRefCitation author="Austin, DF" journalOrPublisher="Canotia" pageId="198" pageNumber="199" pagination="79 - 106" refId="B12" refString="Austin, DF, 2006. Noteworthy distributions and additions in Southwestern Convolvulaceae. Canotia 2 (3): 79 - 106" title="Noteworthy distributions and additions in Southwestern Convolvulaceae." volume="2" year="2006">Austin 2006</bibRefCitation>
: 79); Mexico: Baja California (
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Raven et al.</emphasis>
12670).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="120" pageNumber="121" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="120" pageNumber="121">
Although separated geographically from related species, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="L. M. Perry, Rhodora 33: 76. 1931. (Perry" authorityYear="1931" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Convolvulus simulans" order="Solanales" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="simulans">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Convolvulus simulans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is very close to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="L., Syst. Nat. ed. 12, 3: 229. 1768. (Linnaeus" authorityYear="1768" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Convolvulus pentapetaloides" order="Solanales" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pentapetaloides">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Convolvulus pentapetaloides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and its allies morphologically and this is confirmed by our molecular studies which show they all belong to a single clade (
<bibRefCitation author="Williams, BRM" journalOrPublisher="Taxon" pageId="214" pageNumber="215" pagination="1287 - 1306" publicationUrl="10.12705/636.9" refId="B388" refString="Williams, BRM, Mitchell, TC, Wood, JRI, Harris, DJ, Scotland, RW, Carine, MA, 2014. Integrating DNA barcode data in a monograph of Convolvulus L. Taxon 63: 1287 - 1306, DOI: 10.12705/636.9" title="Integrating DNA barcode data in a monograph of Convolvulus L." url="10.12705/636.9" volume="63" year="2014">Williams et al. 2014</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
